In SMIPS we host all EPIC review files, now under development.
At the birth of an EPIC responsible dev will place here Noam's design review template incorp own EPIC design ideas.
Prior to the Design Review meeting on  EPIC, responsible dev will answer here any questions, to help others prepare.
Design reviews becomes final, ad ready for execution, once Noam and resposible dev. delt with all outstanding issues raised. 
